prompt: A sleek black and white Tshirt  perfect for summers casual vibes
revised_prompt: Imagine a stylish summer T-shirt, characterized by its sleek design. The design is a clean blend of black and white, evoking a sense of casual elegance perfect for warm summer weather. The T-shirt maintains its simplistic approach, suggesting versatility in pairing with other wardrobe items. Further detailing, however, reveals more attention to style, with the black and white color scheme ingeniously laid out to provide a flattering silhouette for the wearer. The shirt is promising to catch eyes, while also comfortable for those hot, lazy days of summer.

prompt: A flowing  floralprinted chiffon shirt with a Vneck and loose  oversized fit  perfect for a casual yet elegant look
revised_prompt: A flowing shirt made of floral-printed chiffon. The shirt exhibits a V-neck design and has a loose, oversized fit. The style of this garment is casual yet carries a certain elegance, making it a versatile piece for various occasions.

prompt: A sophisticated and elegant evening look  featuring a luxurious cashmere coat  a shimmering swan necklace  and a touch of subtle grey
revised_prompt: Create an image of a sophisticated and elegant evening look, complete with a luxurious cashmere coat in a muted tone. The coat has delicate detailing and high-quality stitching. Accessorizing the look is a shimmering swan necklace, a stunning piece of jewelry that stands out against the backdrop of the coat. It is simple, yet conveys an air of sophistication. To round off the look, there are subtle hints of grey added through accessories or apparel, enhancing the overall elegance without overpowering the ensemble.
